  m_Name: chap3_5
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LevelStoryData
  levelName: 
  introLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "\u0110\u1EBFn r\u1ED3i sao , \u0111i\u1EC3m k\u1EBFt th\xFAc\u2026"
  - speaker: Slime
    text: "nh\xE2n lo\u1EA1i\u2026 virut\u2026 ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t\u2026"
  - speaker: Lena
    text: "!??? Ch\xFAng bi\u1EBFt n\xF3i sao ??"
  - speaker: Dr.Elias
    text: "ch\u1EADc c\xF3 v\u1EBB nh\u01B0 ch\xFAng  ta ph\u1EA3i nhanh l\xEAn th\xF4i"
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "th\u1EE9 to l\u1EDBn \u0111ang c\u1ED1 chui ra kia l\xE0 g\xEC v\u1EADy\u2026"
  outroLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "Khe n\u1EE9t \u0111\xE3 \u0111\xF3ng... Th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi h\u1EADu t\u1EADn
      th\u1EBF t\u1EA1m y\xEAn b\xECnh. Nh\u01B0ng n\u1EBFu l\u0169 slime \u0111\xE3
      ti\u1EBFn h\xF3a \u0111\u1EBFn m\u1EE9c hi\u1EC3u v\xE0 n\xF3i ti\u1EBFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi...
      Li\u1EC7u ch\xFAng c\xF3 quay l\u1EA1i, m\u1EA1nh m\u1EBD h\u01A1n? Shadow...
      Anh xin l\u1ED7i m\xE0y. Nh\xE2n lo\u1EA1i b\u1EA5t l\u1EF1c \u0111\u1EBFn
      th\u1EBF sao? Ch\xFAng ta... c\xF3 th\u1EF1c s\u1EF1 th\u1EAFng?"
